title: Swingball 5 in 1 Outdoor Game Set - Includes, Soccer, Volleyball, Tailball Tennis and a Flying Disc
features: SWINGBALL SET: Get outside and play with the Swingball 5 in 1 Set! In an easy-to-carry case, you can play swingball, soccer, volleyball, tail ball, and disc toss with family and friends.

PLAY ANYWHERE: With the all surface base, these sports can be played anywhere, outside or indoors. All items store in the base which becomes a carry case with handle. For those ages 6 years old and up.
FUN FOR ALL: It’s a whole lot of fun for the entire family! With a height adjustable pole, children, teens, and adults can play. Boys and girls can play outdoors with the Swingball 5 in 1 Set.

EASY SETUP AND STORAGE: The new two part base with easy peel lid can be weighted with sand or water. The integrated balancing feet offer amazing stability for every surface. Its compact storage case is designed to save space and can be stacked vertically or self-stand on shelf.
ENDLESS PLAY: It comes with all the stuff you need - balls, equipment, and unique y-net - all in a cool, portable base. It’s a perfect summer activity idea for when you want to get out and play.
description: The ultimate Swingball game with 3 modes and 5 ways to play. This set has everything you need to keep families entertained all year round with Swingball, Soccer Swingball, Volleyball, Tailball Badminton and a Flying Disc. The all surface base with unique “Y” Net can be played anywhere, indoors or outdoors. All items store in the base which becomes a carry case with handle. • Ages 6+
